{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"a1b2c","text":"Dice Roller","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d3e4f","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"g5h6i","text":"Need to roll some dice for your tabletop game? This interactive dice roller lets you customize the number of dice and the number of sides on each die. Whether you're playing D&D with 20-sided dice or Yahtzee with standard 6-sided dice, this tool has you covered.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"j7k8l","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"m9n0o","text":"Select your configuration and click \"Roll Dice\" to see the results. The widget will show each individual die result as well as the total sum. Perfect for quick rolls when you don't have physical dice handy!","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}